text: Ewe Omurumwa, Abakhasi abasuubili nibakhwitsila	nibakhulaka	mbu shibalatsokaasia shiosi shiosi nende Nyasaye tawe, neshibaleebatawe,nohombashibalayeya tawe nohomba shibaleera Abana babu tawe, nohomba shibalarera akokhuchikha akarulana hakari wemikhono nende ebilenje biabu, Nohomba shibalakhwikana mumalayi tawe, lakana ninabo, ne obasabile eshileshelo khu Nyasaye , toto Nyasaye Nomulesheli muno Wobukoosia po
